OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1778367991
OL,3,CStolen tractor crashed into house in
OL,4,Cmiddle of the night
OL,6,FPolice are investigating after a
OL,7,Fstolen tractor crashed into the front
OL,8,Fa Teesside house in the middle of the
OL,9,Fnight.
OL,11,FThe tractor, said to have been stolen
OL,12,Ffrom Yarm, crashed into the property
OL,13,Fon Priory Road in Middlesbrough in the
OL,14,Fearly hours of Saturday morning (9
OL,15,FMay).
OL,17,FCleveland Police cordoned off the road
OL,18,Fwith several residents evacuated from
OL,19,Ftheir homes as a precaution.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
