FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1778367991
OL,3,CStolen tractor crashed into house in
OL,4,Cmiddle of the night
OL,6,FNo one was injured as the house was
OL,7,Fsaid to be unoccupied.
OL,9,FPolice are currently treating the
OL,10,Fincident as deliberate. Those inside
OL,11,Fthe vehicle are said to have left the
OL,12,Fscene.
OL,14,FDetective Chief Inspector John Bonner,
OL,15,Ffrom Middlesbrough CID, said: "Shortly
OL,16,Fafter 1am on Saturday 9 May, police
OL,17,Freceived reports of a tractor being
OL,18,Fdriven into a house on Priory Road in
OL,19,FMiddlesbrough.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1778367991
OL,3,CStolen tractor crashed into house in
OL,4,Cmiddle of the night
OL,6,F"Those inside the tractor immediately
OL,7,Ffled from the area. The property is
OL,8,Funoccupied therefore no one suffered
OL,9,Fany injury, however, neighbouring
OL,10,Fproperties were evacuated as a
OL,11,Fprecaution and will return once it has
OL,12,Fbeen deemed safe."
OL,14,FHe added: "We are currently treating
OL,15,Fthis as deliberate, and a scene is in
OL,16,Fplace while the investigation is
OL,17,Fongoing. I'd ask members of the public
OL,18,Fto avoid the area where possible.
OL,19,FAdditional patrols will be carried out
OL,20,Fin the area over the weekend to
OL,21,Fprovide reassurance to the community.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1778367991
OL,3,CStolen tractor crashed into house in
OL,4,Cmiddle of the night
OL,6,F"I appeal to anyone who has
OL,7,Finformation, dash cam or doorbell
OL,8,Ffootage of the tractor, which was
OL,9,Fstolen from Yarm, in the run up to it
OL,10,Fbeing taken and driven to
OL,11,FMiddlesbrough, and the damage it did,
OL,12,Fto please get in touch quoting
OL,13,Freference number 087639.You can
OL,14,Fprovide information anonymously by
OL,15,Fcalling Crimestoppers on 0800 555 111."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
